Principal Deputy National Security Advisor Jon Finer met with United Nations Senior Humanitarian and Reconstruction Coordinator for Gaza Sigrid Kaag to discuss increasing humanitarian assistance for civilians in Gaza. They also talked about sustainable solutions to meet the needs of Gazan civilians in the long term. Mr. Finer also had a meeting with UN Under-Secretary-General for Political and Peacebuilding Affairs Rosemary DiCarlo to discuss U.S.-UN coordination on Gaza, including support for Ms. Kaag's efforts.